nd the agency=E2=80=99s Journey to Mars could all go away, very quickly, at t=
he whim of some future President or Congressional majority. Mired in the muc=
k of politics, NASA may not manage to land even one crew of astronauts on Ma=
rs by 2035=E2=80=94let alone three.</p>
<p>Then again, by the 2030s, there may be good reasons to avoid landing on M=
